      .character-row.vena
        .grid
          .row
            .image-col.col.col-tablet-8.col-laptop-5.col-tablet-offset-2.col-laptop-offset-0.col-desktop-offset-1
              img(src='/assets/images/windy-meadow/venasmile.png')
            .text-col.col.col-laptop-7.col-desktop-5
              h3.character-header Vena
              p
                strong &#32;Vena
                |, the huntress, has an opportunity to start a lucrative job among the city merchants, and to leave her home for years to come. Before she decides what to do next, she needs to figure out her relationship with her over controlling father, and learn what it is that she truly wants from her life.

      .character-row.fabel
        .grid
          .row
            .text-col.col.col-laptop-7.col-desktop-5.col-desktop-offset-1
              h3.character-header Fabel
              p
